  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give Trauma-Informed Care to Orphans in Macedonia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Lighthouse of Hope MK exists to provide care for orphans in North Macedonia. We are providing hope for these orphans, and their caregivers, in three primary ways: Family-Style Group Homes, Foster and Adoptive Family Support, and Education. This project seeks to see vulnerable children raised in a healthy, loving, and educational environment. We provide them with a warm, safe place with trauma-informed caregivers, giving the children the ability to form healthy attachments and relationships.</narrative>
  </description>
